sub_title: Student Consultant | IBR 2023 Brazil & Colombia. MSc Change Management at the University of Groningen
summary:
Currently studying Bedrijfskunde at the University of Groningen. I also just completed an extracurricular course in entrepreneurship.
I am interested in sustainable innovations and entrepreneurship. 
I am an ambitious, social and flexible person with a drive to make the most of the projects that I participate in. Furthermore, I am not afraid to dive into something new and unknown.
